OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry start
OL,6,Fthis evening before outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fspread from the southwest. Then cloudy
OL,8,Fovernight with spells of rain, turning
OL,9,Fpersistent across the west later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FRain spreading northeast for a
OL,12,Ftime in the morning. Then turning
OL,13,Fbrighter with a few showers,
OL,14,Foccasionally heavy later. Brisk
OL,15,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRather
OL,18,Fcloudy with showers on Saturday.
OL,19,FMainly dry with sunny spells on Sunday
OL,20,Fand Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
